EDIT: Sweet. Front page. Send tiddies, I guess.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/U5ASoH2</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[OptionThirty]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Tired of my mom</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/UFcGJYy</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3LNewuW.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Tldr: My mom is a free-loader, control freak, and I am kicking her out.

My mom is 70 years old. in 2008 she had back surgery (L3-L5 fusion) and cannot work, but she is active. 2 years ago she wanted to move into my (large) house and said she would not interfere with my life, just live quietly. That has changed rather quickly. She does not pay any bills, never help me with mortgage, just helped me on few home improvements. I always tried to keep her happy, we went on many roadtrips, she saw more of America in last 2 years than her whole life. she  is not required to help me around house, as I can manage my self, but I did allow her to help me to keep her busy and occupied. She tries to control me, makes decisions for me, tells me what I can and cannot do in my life, in my house. When she is mad, she accuses me of stealing her things (that I would have no use for).  I cannot take this any more. She has money to move out, even to buy own condo, but would not help me with my bills. I know she's my mom, but the way she treats me is ridiculous.

Edit: this wasn't planned on being viral, this was supposed to be me venting in usersub... but thanks all for support.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/UFcGJYy</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AloneInTheWoods]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Thursday meme dump</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Q9RiETw</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6hrEu02.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Nice</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nMXtBpk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZXhK58X.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UbBbFEJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/snyNDyK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/s3qc0UE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OBP869o.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FIMg1Tc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ajatIBV.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LqGjuoH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I think very few people would look fashionable in that thing</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/i2TDrXk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VDRqT3b.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RSupOB1.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: